{"tid":1806423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[不完美可接受]今日到底集會定遊行？","createTime":"2020-01-01T09:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T10:13:47.000Z","uid":35273,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"97f32aea2c7f51d9b48a9eae040bcdb07333ccba","tid":1806423,"uid":35273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T09:54:39.000Z","msg":"第一 唔係屌 希望想改善<br />\n<br />\n今日1315 1330左右到 已經都人山人海<br />\n用咗兩個鐘先到草皮 見到係到播歌叫口號<br />\n咁點樣點人數？<br />\n<br />\n已經有人係出邊企到暈都未開始行<br />\n之後又話取消<br />\n<br />\n維園附近又無人又標示 <br />\n有個鬼佬記者問我都唔知今日係點<br />\n到底點解唔行 啲人流咁散<br />\n但隊頭又可以行到終點<br />\n<br />\n我覺得不完美可接受 希望下次可以控制好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514efcdd31e0605040b02fe24b396e0e8533d350","tid":1806423,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">下次遊行主題要係真普選呀<br />\n<br />\n廢除功能組別 2020雙普選</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廢除功能組別 2020雙普選</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廢除功能組別 2020雙普選</span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"0bac124e8d88274058d9b59b97dd26b3de2339a5","tid":1806423,"uid":315760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T10:01:52.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n老實講見到咁多人係開心嘅<br />\n<br />\n但見到身邊有啲公公婆婆同我地一齊企咁耐，幾個錢冇行過，替佢地覺得辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162967ef4d4dea1b890d6cc0ebc7afc77a48c7b1","tid":1806423,"uid":35273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T10:12:05.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n 做好多"},{"pid":"608a922adcee8402982f5b3e402a0cf1f1a3b3f7","tid":1806423,"uid":252510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T10:17:32.000Z","msg":"其實由3點起遊行開始 維園已經陸續行緊出去<br />\n不過 <em><strong>都係太多人插隊</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n利申：維園近隊頭位置 由兩點企到五點先出到維園"},{"pid":"3c6dc6844d12f2313ce7965e562f0c0da5bab2f1","